Location

The Fancy Clothes Store is a shop in south-eastern Varrock. It is owned and run by Asyff. The shop sells needles and thread and different kinds of clothes such as gloves, boots, capes and hats. The store is also the only place where players can obtain hunter clothing, through the Custom Fur Clothing panel, some of which increases one's Thieving abilities or provides weight reduction.
